# Add Slack Notification in Jenkinsfile

## Step 18: Update Jenkinsfile

```groovy id="h8h9k2"
pipeline {
    agent any

    stages {

        stage('Build') {
            steps {
                echo 'Building Application'
            }
        }
    }

    post {

        success {
            slackSend (
                channel: '#general',
                message: 'Build Successful'
            )
        }

        failure {
            slackSend (
                channel: '#general',
                message: 'Build Failed'
            )
        }
    }
}
```

